title: How Lamar Jackson keeps getting better & what's going on with the Rams?
itunes:title: How Lamar Jackson keeps getting better & what's going on with the Rams?
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. First, the guys recap the Ravens' Monday Night Football win against the Rams, as they start off by analyzing how Ravens' QB Lamar Jackson keeps getting better (2:08). Next, the duo look at what's going on with the Rams and explain why the team hasn't been playing as well as last season (15:45). After, the pair discuss which college coaches could potentially make a jump to the NFL (26:48). To wrap up, DJ and Bucky talk about college players they are studying and also give an evaluation of a few guys (37:21).
